parameters:
Fotizona Guard: Lady Caron released a monster... I don't
want to believe it, but we have to accept it.

Fotizona Guard: This may just be a consolation, but please
take it. We will definitely protect the public order of the
city along with the supporters of the prince.

Fotizona Guard: I'm glad Storge-san came. We were about to
engage in a battle with the supporters of the prince.

Fotizona Guard: I thought I could take it easy by moving
from Camps... but it seems like I am destined to fight on
the front lines for the Empire.

Fotizona Guard: To be honest, guarding here is easy. I used
to be at the campus, but it was tough with all the thieves.

Fotizona Guard: I can't stand seeing this city turned into a
battlefield... I will fight too.

Fotizona Guard: No problems today either! I pray that days
like this will continue forever.

Prince's soldier: We must defeat Caron. We cannot allow
monsters to roam freely in this town!

Fotizona Guard: I fight for this town, I'm not just a
private soldier of Lady Caron.

Fotizona Guard: In the treasure chest over there is a
treasure book... Oh my! I shouldn't have been talking to
such a beautiful lady.

Prince's Army Soldier: It seems that the battle is
intensifying even outside of Fotizona. Please take care of
subduing the dragons and Caron. Thank you in advance.

Prince's Army Captain: I was amazed by Storge-san's
negotiation skills. We will cooperate with the city guards
to reduce the number of casualties, even if it's just one
person.

Prince's Army Captain: Please take this with you and carry
our feelings together.

Prince's Army Captain: May the blessings of the goddess
Actina be with you! We pray for everyone's safety and
victory!
Storge of Love: Thank goodness, are you all safe?
Clea: ...It seems like you know about Mr. Shimos, huh?

Storge of Love: I witnessed it... No, rather, I fought
alongside him until the end.

Storge of Love: It's sad, but the monsters in the city were
defeated to some extent after all...

Storge of Love: It seems that some of the nobles from the
Queen's faction are heading this way.
Thief Nora: I-Is it, like, really bad!?
Clea: Is the command here okay?

Storge of Love: Who do you think I am? I'm making the nobles
from the Queen's faction defect and keeping them occupied.

Storge of Love: Besides, there are also soldiers from the
Prince's faction here. It's not a good idea to have too many
commanders in this situation.

Storge of Love: Besides, we absolutely have to avenge Mr.
Shimos.

\CL Nora has become able to use the support skill
Encouragement \C[0]. \|

Voice Priestess Phoni: Haa... I'm managing to hold back the
monsters, but I'm reaching my limit--

Voice Priestess Phoni: I'm completely fine! I'm okay now,
what should I do!?
Voice of Compassion Storge: Hey, could it be that Phoni...?
Priestess Sophia: Hehe, let's stop for now.

Voice Priestess Phoni: I heard the voice and understood. It
possesses a power even greater than the previous dragon.

Voice Priestess Phoni: I just... felt like my power to
control the monsters is weak, or more accurately, it feels
like it's being suppressed.

Voice Priestess Phoni: It's almost as if someone is
intentionally causing the monsters to go berserk...

Mage Relm: I believe this is the work of Caron. She was
conducting research on that kind of 'manipulation'.
Clea: Phoni, could you come up to the rooftop with me?

Voice Priestess Phoni: Of course, Clea. As a new priestess,
I will also fight alongside the dragons!

\CL Clea has acquired the support skill Voice of the Pure
\C[0] and can now use it \|.
